---
import Layout from '../layouts/BarringtonLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Flat Tire Repair Barrington, IL | 24/7 Emergency Service | We Come To You" description="Stuck with a flat tire in Barrington? Don't tow it! We provide 24/7 mobile flat tire repair at your location. Fast response, puncture patching, and spare installation.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-barrington-primary to-barrington-primary-dark text-white py-16 md:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486262715619-67b85e0b08d3?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80')] bg-cover bg-center opacity-20"></div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">Emergency Flat Tire Repair in Barrington</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 mb-8">Fast, reliable roadside assistance. We fix your flat right where you are.</p>
            <a href="tel:8475558473" class="inline-block bg-barrington-accent hover:bg-barrington-accent-hover text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
                Call Now: (847) 555-8473
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Don't Wait for a Tow Truck</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                There is never a convenient time for a flat tire. Whether you're heading to work in the morning, picking up kids from Barrington High School, or stuck on Northwest Highway late at night, a flat tire can ruin your day. Traditional solutions involve waiting hours for a tow truck to drag your car to a shop that might not even be open.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-800 mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-barrington-accent pl-4 bg-slate-50 py-2">
                <strong>Barrington Mobile Tire Pros offers a better way.</strong> Our fully equipped mobile tire vans come directly to your location—home, office, or roadside—to repair or replace your tire on the spot.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Our Flat Repair Services</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Puncture Repair</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">We use permanent patch-plug repairs for nail and screw punctures in the tread area. This is the safest, industry-standard repair method.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Spare Tire Installation</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">If your tire is shredded or has sidewall damage, we'll safely install your spare tire to get you moving again.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Valve Stem Replacement</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Leaking valve stems are a common cause of slow leaks. We can replace them quickly and re-pressurize your tire.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Rim Cleaning & Sealing</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Corrosion on the rim bead can cause air loss. We clean and seal the bead area to ensure an airtight fit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Why Choose Mobile Repair?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-12">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Faster Response</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">We are local to Barrington and can often arrive in under 60 minutes.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Cost-Effective</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">Avoid expensive towing fees. We fix the problem on-site.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1">check_circle</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong class="block text-slate-900">Safe</strong>
                        <span class="text-slate-600">Stay in your car or a safe location while we do the dangerous work on the roadside.</span>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
                <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Stranded right now?</p>
                <a href="tel:8475558473" class="inline-block bg-barrington-accent hover:bg-barrington-accent-hover text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-colors">
                    Call (847) 555-8473 for Help
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
